IRS990.ActivityOrMissionDesc: PLANNED PARENTHOOD SOUTH ATLANTIC, INC. IS A PRIVATE, NONPROFIT FAMILY PLANNING AGENCY THAT RESPECTS AND PROTECTS THE RIGHTS OF EACH MAN AND WOMAN TO MAKE INFORMED REPRODUCTIVE DECISIONS. OUR MISSION IS TO PROVIDE ACCESSIBLE, HIGH-QUALITY HEALTH CARE AND INFORMATION TO CLIENTS AND TO SERVE AS ADVOCATE AND EDUCATOR TO THE COMMUNITY ON RESPONSIBLE HUMAN SEXUALITY. WE HAVE OFFICES IN NORTH CAROLINA, SOUTH CAROLINA, VIRGINIA AND WEST VIRGINIA. PLANNED PARENTHOOD SOUTH ATLANTIC, INC. IS AN AFFILIATE OF PLANNED PARENTHOOD FEDERATION OF AMERICA, INC., THE WORLD'S LARGEST AND MOST TRUSTED VOLUNTARY REPRODUCTIVE HEALTH CARE ORGANIZATION. FOUNDED BY MARGARET SANGER IN 1916 AS AMERICA'S FIRST BIRTH CONTROL CLINIC, PLANNED PARENTHOOD BELIEVES IN EVERYONE'S RIGHT TO CHOOSE WHEN OR WHETHER TO HAVE A CHILD, THAT EVERY CHILD SHOULD BE WANTED AND LOVED, AND THAT WOMEN SHOULD BE IN CHARGE OF THEIR OWN DESTINIES.

ProgSrvcAccomActy2Grp.Desc: PLANNED PARENTHOOD SOUTH ATLANTIC SUPPORTS EACH CITIZEN'S RIGHT TO MAKE INFORMED DECISIONS REGARDING HIS OR HER HEALTH. WE HAVE A LARGE NETWORK OF GRASSROOTS SUPPORTERS WHO ARE COMMITTED TO DEFENDING AND INCREASING ACCESS TO FAMILY PLANNING SERVICES, HIGH-QUALITY, NONJUDGMENTAL ABORTION SERVICES, AND MEDICALLY-ACCURATE SEXUALITY EDUCATION.

ProgSrvcAccomActy3Grp.Desc: PLANNED PARENTHOOD SOUTH ATLANTIC BELIEVES THAT INFORMED CHOICES BEGINS WITH EDUCATION. OUR PROGRAMS ARE INNOVATIVE, BOLD, AND EFFECTIVE TOOLS FOR PREVENTING ADOLESCENT PREGNANCY AND PROMOTING LIFE-LONG HEALTHY DECISION MAKING.
